      • getTransformed

        public NondetModel getTransformed(ProbModelTransformationOperator transformation)
                           throws PrismException
        Apply the given model transformation, specified as a ProbModelTransformationOperator, on this model and return the resulting, transformed model.
        This convenience method does the transformation via a NondetModelTransformationOperation that is constructed on-the-fly from the given transformation. For this to work properly, the getTrans method has to preserve the action information, i.e., simply augment the state space in some way.
        As an example, a simple product construction with a deterministic automaton would work fine, as that does not change the structure of the transitions.
        Overrides:
        getTransformed in class ProbModel
        Parameters:
        transformation - the transformation operator
        Returns:
        the transformed model (needs to be cleared after use)
        Throws:
        PrismException
